services. That
means that for an estimated
1,800 veterans

43:16.661 --> 43:21.399 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
like Jason, they will also have
to spend tens
of thousands of dollars to get
pregnant and

43:21.432 --> 43:23.201 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
start a family.

43:23.234 --> 43:27.138 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Senator Patty Murray wants that
to change.
This Democrat from Washington
state sits on

43:27.171 --> 43:31.709 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
the Senate Veterans Affairs
Committee, and
she wrote a bill that would lift
the VA's

43:31.742 --> 43:35.246 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
IVF ban. But for six years, her
efforts have
been blocked.

43:35.279 --> 43:38.983 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
SEN. PATTY MURRAY (D),
Washington: To me,
when someone goes off to fight a
war for us,

43:39.016 --> 43:44.288 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
a man or a woman, we have an
obligation as
the country to make them whole
again, as whole

43:44.322 --> 43:49.827 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
as we can. And, certainly,
having a family,
having children, having that
kind of quality

43:49.861 --> 43:53.764 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
of life that a lot of Americans
want is something
that we should make sure they
get.

43:53.798 --> 43:57.235 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: Why is it that
the VA doesn't
pay for these services now?

43:57.268 --> 44:03.274 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
SEN. PATTY MURRAY: I have been
told that it
is because of the cost. I
believe that that

44:03.307 --> 44:08.346 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
shouldn't be an issue. This is
something that
is a cost of war and that, as
Americans, we

44:08.379 --> 44:15.453 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
should do what we can for the
people who served
our country. So, the stated
reason is money,

44:15.486 --> 44:16.754 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
but I'm skeptical.

44:16.787 --> 44:18.890 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: What do you
think the issue
it really is?

44:18.923 --> 44:24.529 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
SEN. PATTY MURRAY: It is hard to
get anyone
to say anything past cost. I
would say to

44:24.562 --> 44:28.266 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
them, let's get over the cost.
If there's
another issue, tell us what it
is.

44:28.299 --> 44:32.637 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: So, what is
the cost? One
estimate says covering IVF and
other fertility

44:32.670 --> 44:39.176 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
treatments for veterans for five
years would
be $578 million. Some IVF
advocates say that

44:39.210 --> 44:40.945 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
estimate is inflated.

44:40.978 --> 44:44.348 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
We reached out to the two
Republicans who
run the Veterans Affairs
Committees in the

44:44.382 --> 44:48.452 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
House and the Senate. Neither
would speak
with us. Republican Congressman
Jeff Miller

44:48.486 --> 44:53.024 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
from Florida, chairman of the
House VA Committee,
gave us a statement saying he
was trying to

44:53.057 --> 44:57.261 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
balance the needs of veterans
with the concerns
over IVF.

44:57.295 --> 45:02.099 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
Several sources told the
"NewsHour" that these
concerns over IVF apparently
come from pro-life

45:02.133 --> 45:06.571 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
organizations who object to the
treatments.
These groups argue that, because
some of the

45:06.604 --> 45:13.010 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
embryos created or stored during
IVF sometimes
get destroyed, IVF is then
similar to abortion.

45:13.044 --> 45:16.414 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
We reached out to the main
pro-life groups
to talk about their concerns,
but they all

45:16.447 --> 45:18.182 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
declined our requests.

45:18.215 --> 45:22.219 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
SEN. PATTY MURRAY: What I would
answer to
that is that this is a decision
each one of

45:22.253 --> 45:26.691 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
these men and woman have to make
on their
own. And if they decide this is
the way that

45:26.724 --> 45:30.962 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
they can have a family and
become whole again,
that decision should be up to
them.

45:30.995 --> 45:38.336 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But our country shouldn't be
deciding for
one philosophy, if it's a
religious philosophy,

45:38.369 --> 45:44.075 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
a ban on all Americans who
served our country
in having the ability to have a
child.

45:44.108 --> 45:48.512 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: It appears
unlikely Congress
will change the VA's policy
before the next

45:48.546 --> 45:53.284 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
election. But for young veterans
and their
families who struggle to afford
IVF, time

45:53.317 --> 45:55.019 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
is very short.

45:55.052 --> 45:58.022 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DR. GILBERT MOTTLA, Shady Grove
Fertility:
We're really talking about some
1,800 Iraq

45:58.055 --> 46:06.297 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
and Afghanistan veterans who are
now aging.
This one group of war injured,
we really need

46:06.330 --> 46:11.769 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
to move this legislation forward
and get these
individuals the coverage they
need before

46:11.802 --> 46:13.938 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
they lose their own reproductive
potential.

46:13.971 --> 46:17.475 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: Doctor Gilbert
Mottla is
a fertility doctor in Maryland
who works with

46:17.508 --> 46:22.413 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
military families. He's pushing
the VA to
